}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_transmutation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "Self"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 1 hour"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a jade circlet worth 1,500+ GP"}, "description": {"value": "You shape-shift into another creature for the duration or until you take a Magic action to shape-shift into a different eligible form. The new form must be of a creature that has a Challenge Rating no higher than your level or Challenge Rating. You must have seen the sort of creature before, and it can't be a Construct or an Undead.\n\nWhen you shape-shift, you gain a number of Temporary Hit Points equal to the Hit Points of the form. The spell ends early if you have no Temporary Hit Points left.\n\nYour game statistics are replaced by the stat block of the chosen form, but you retain your creature type; alignment; personality; Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma scores; Hit Points; Hit Point Dice; proficiencies; and ability to communicate. If you have the Spellcasting feature, you retain it too.\n\nUpon shape-shifting, you determine whether your equipment drops to the ground or changes in size and shape to fit the new form while you're in it"}, "classes": {"value": ["druid", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.641740"}, "id": "shapechange"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Control Weather"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_8"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_transmutation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "10 minutes"}, "range": {"value": "Self (5-mile radius)"}, "duration": {"value": "Concentration, up to 8 hours"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "burning incense"}, "description": {"value": "You take control of the weather within 5 miles of you for the duration. You must be outdoors to cast this spell. Moving to a place where you don't have a clear path to the sky ends the spell early.\n\nWhen you cast the spell, you change the current weather conditions, which are determined by the GM based on the climate and season. You can change precipitation, temperature, and wind. It takes 1d4 x 10 minutes for the new conditions to take effect. Once they do so, you can change the conditions again. When the spell ends, the weather gradually returns to normal.\n\nWhen you change the weather conditions, find a current condition on the following tables and change its stage by one, up or down. When changing the wind, you can change its direction.\n\nPrecipitation:\n\nStage 1 - Clear\nStage 2 - Light clouds\nStage 3 - Overcast or ground fog\nStage 4 - Rain, hail, or snow\nStage 5 - Torrential rain, driving hail, or blizzard\n\nTemperature:\n\nStage 1 - Heat wave\nStage 2 - Hot\nStage 3 - Warm\nStage 4 - Cool\nStage 5 - Cold\nStage 6 - Arctic cold\n\nWind:\n\nStage 1 - Calm\nStage 2 - Moderate wind\nStage 3 - Strong wind\nStage 4 - Gale\nStage 5 - Storm"}, "classes": {"value": ["cleric", "druid", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.639053"}, "id": "control_weather"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Ice Storm"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_4"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_evocation"}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "300 feet"}, "duration": {"value": "Instantaneous"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "material": {"value": true}, "components": {"value": "a mitten"}, "description": {"value": "Hail falls in a 20-foot-radius, 40-foot-high Cylinder centered on a point within range. Each creature in the Cylinder makes a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 2d10 Bludgeoning damage and 4d6 Cold damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\nHailstones turn ground in the Cylinder into Difficult Terrain until the end of your next turn"}, "higher_level_description": {"value": "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th level or higher, the bludgeoning damage increases by 1d10 for each slot level above 4th."}, "classes": {"value": ["druid", "sorcerer", "fighter", "rogue", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "levelled_damage_dice", "stats": {"level": {"value": 4}, "damage_dice": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "damage_dice", "stats": {"dices": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "dice_roll", "stats": {"dice_amount": {"value": 2}, "dice_type": {"value": "d10"}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.656808"}, "id": "b52e8e7b-f77e-4006-88ad-e8f64f18c909"}}]}, "damage_type": {"value": "bludgeoning"}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.656813"}, "id": "462d932e-d656-4223-b902-ee36ff0fcd46"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "damage_dice", "stats": {"dices": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "dice_roll", "stats": {"dice_amount": {"value": 4}, "dice_type": {"value": "d6"}, "id": "3c79a3a8-af0e-40ae-a5a5-a52db66d9293"}}]}, "damage_type": {"value": "cold"}, "id": "81897d3e-0e87-4f66-9677-e336f6727921"}}]}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.656818"}, "id": "0e630b7a-2877-459a-9359-d2e511be1bd8"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "levelled_damage_dice", "stats": {"level": {"value": 5}, "damage_dice": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "damage_dice", "stats": {"dices": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "dice_roll", "stats": {"dice_amount": {"value": 3}, "dice_type": {"value": "d10"}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.656827"}, "id": "c1b0d2fb-aa49-4f95-9007-24d253e4b412"}}]}, "damage_type": {"value": "bludgeoning"}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.656831"}, "id": "d4882637-8368-401f-b47a-d515e7beb496"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "damage_d